            f"The proposed solution to the mystery of {t['mystery']} is creative, logical, and well-supported by the linguistic reconstruction.",
            "The analysis shows a strong grasp of interdisciplinary thinking, combining linguistics, history, and problem-solving.",
            "The response acknowledges limitations and proposes valid methods for validation of the reconstruction and solution.",
            "The writing is clear, well-structured, and uses technical terminology appropriately."
